<br>
&quot;He has concealed guns all over his body,&quot; Mahmoud said. <br>
<br>
&quot;He also has panic buttons to press if he even suspects somebody is about to attack him.&quot; <br>
<br>
Israeli intelligence sources have hinted that the deal with Mahmoud included smuggling his family out of Iraq. <br>
<br>
Mossad agents have done this before. <br>
<br>
